Summary: 
 * Merge from SysteMoC--devel--0.8
 - Eliminated push_interface, can be implemented by add_interfaces directly
 - Changed visibility level of bind(sc_interface &) and bind(smoc_sysc_port &)
   to protected like equivalent functionallity in SystemC
 - Add public visible bind(<concrete interface> &) and
   bind(<concrete port type> &) to smoc_port_base<IFACE>
 - Some code unification from smoc_port_in_base and smoc_port_out_base now in smoc_port_base
 - Moved tokenIsValid from smoc_port_in_base to smoc_port_in due to its
   dependency on the channel access type, i.e., not all channel access
   types may have a tokenIsValid method.
 - Eliminated unused CommitCount DExpr evaluator
 - Fixed assertions in QueueFRVWPtr fpp
